{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the powers of your flashlight to light up the shadow creatures that roam trought the forest and seek your way out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/SteamDescription1.gif?t=1731638988\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the flashlight as your main weapon of defeating the shadow creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shoot, dodge or counter the bullet hell-like attacks of all your enemies to survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gain Light Drops by defeating enemies to become stronger or use them to buy items, upgrades and costumes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate through the 5 areas of the forest to find your way out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat strong enemies to rescue the spirits of children trapped in the shadow's realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the secret pages hidden throught the forest to learn more about events that transpired before your arrival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new powers and use them to clear puzzles blocking your path.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/SteamDescription2.gif?t=1731638988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>-Have you ever heard stories of monsters living under the bed?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>- What about legends of shadow figures who kidnap inocent children?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a quiet night like any other, a little girl had the misfortune of experiencing the visit of a shadow being - The Forgotten - and is taken to a dark forest in the realm of this creature. Now she has to find a way out before the shadows take her soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate throught the forest with help of your new friends, fight with a magical flashlight to be your light and learn about the fate of your long lost sister and her sudden disapearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/SteamDescription3.gif?t=1731638988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Someone Was Here","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/a895ccc6ae13f9913929feef81c33b559dfd53bc.jpg"},{"name":"Horrors Of The Past","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/dcea0932a43eb3d5cc93c460ea7847ce9ddae225.jpg"},{"name":"It Started Like This","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/48698fb1d4701759fa4be1c4c993bd737388ef9b.jpg"},{"name":"The Law of Equivalent Exchange","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/0fff7f79d3dd5a306bdc82ad1e9abf9aef53070c.jpg"},{"name":"Better Safe Than Sorry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/fb8452b38f6f2181cc1d8d472612de064b1ce333.jpg"},{"name":"Get Sturdy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/a6f117a0f7fe83646b043f04ecbe3325ada92760.jpg"},{"name":"The Ultimate Cosplayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/1c4dafc5692509375f0dacc508b952ddf0df8ce7.jpg"},{"name":"Play Your Own Way","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/6c90332cdde27ccc491863352f13ba74e6ecf55a.jpg"},{"name":"Shadow Is The Absence of Light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2208220/f3a2f4